Underscore.js is a utility-belt library for JavaScript that provides support for the usual functional suspects (each, map, reduce, filterâ€¦) without extending any core JavaScript objects.

For Docs, License, Tests, and pre-packed downloads, see: underscorejs.org

Underscore is an open-sourced component of DocumentCloud: github.com/documentcloud

Many thanks to our contributors: github.com/jashkenas/underscore/contributors
